main event: A civilian reported seeing two objects with redded white lights in Lutz, Florida on March 7, 1956.
interesting points: The sighting included two objects that were described as round and baseball-shaped.,The objects were observed for a short time before disappearing.,The report mentioned a possible meteor sighting around the same time.,The conclusion of the report indicated insufficient data for further analysis.,The observation was conducted by civilians who were on duty at the time.
